{
  "stem": "12768.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They wrote back and said, how old are you?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I said 17 and 1/2.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They'd said that you had to be 18, and I said I was 17 and 1/2 and so, physically, I'm strong enough to be able to-- to volunteer.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So they said, OK.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I needed my father's consent.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My father thought that that was a great idea, so he said OK.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In October 1944, I have gotten a ticket to come to Stockholm.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And from Stockholm it was with a train there to go to this camp that we were going to.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And, of course, when I got off the bus, you were in-- in mud up to your ankles already.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I said, oh, my nice clothes and all.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Then that night, we were just given a place to sleep, you know, a bunk, and that was it.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The next day, we were outside.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we got our numbers and papers and everything else.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then we got what they call uniforms, which was not that warm clothes, you know.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And And we had rain and sleet, and soon it begin to snow.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And so it was-- it was hard training every day.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And it was training and training and training.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I don't remember anything else, you know, and sleeping and walking or running, and learning fighting and shooting and going to the shooting range.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And the food was not the-- it was like-- like real army food, you know.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But then, of course, the Swedes, they never ate as good as the Danes.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So it was even worse, you felt.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And many of us got sick from bad food and everything else.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But at least we built up units.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And my two other brothers all-- we were four brothers, actually, that wanted to volunteer.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
